(180, 1, '2015-07-31 05:45:35', '2015-07-31 03:45:35', 'Du hc Nht Bn: Cc kha hc  Nht thng nhp trng vo khong thng 1, 4, 7, 10. Trc khi bc ln my bay, hn cc bn c rt nhiu iu bn khon lo lng cn chun b cho cuc sng du hc sp ti. Nhng li khuyn sau y c l s gip ch phn no cho cc bn khi chun b hnh trang ln ng du hc.\r\n<h3>1. Hnh trang du hc Nht Bn</h3>\r\n<div>Nhng th ti thiu bn cn mang: My tnh, in thoi, my nghe nhc, kim t in, t trang, vn phng phm; thng tin cn bit v nc n du hc nh thi tit, t gi tin t, phong tc tp qun, nhng s in thoi tr gip; h chiu cn thi hn ti thiu 6 thng v th thc nhp cnh (visa), v my bay, giy t bo him, th sinh vin quc t (nu c), mt s nh 4x6 v 3x4 dng cho vic lm cc loi th khi cn, cc giy t lin quan n trng s hc nh th mi hc, thng tin nh  (a ch, in thoi, tn ch nh), ngi n  sn bay (tn, in thoi), tn ngi ph trch sinh vin quc t ti trng n hc, cc giy t lin quan n qu trnh hc tp trc y, h s tim chng, giy t chng minh ti chnh v bn c th cn n khi gia hn kho hc; mt t tin tiu vt trong thi gian u, s in thoi, fax, email cn thit, thuc d phng thng thng nh du xoa, thuc ho, au u, cm st, nh mi, khng sinh, au bng, nh gia nh, bn b v mt s a nhc yu thch v chng s gip bn bt nh nh trong thi gian u; dn tn, a ch ni bn n, s in thoi lin lc ln tt c ti hnh l, ghi li  c ng gi trong mi vali  tin trnh bo trong trng hp hnh l b tht lc, nn kim tra xem hnh l c b qu cn khng trc khi ra sn bay, kim tra  trnh mang nhng  b cm  nc s n hc.</div>\r\n<h3>2. Ti cc sn bay khi i du hc Nht Bn</h3>\r\n<div><strong>Ti sn bay Vit Nam</strong></div>\r\n<div>- Chun b v gi buc hnh l gn gh, chc chn, d gi vi hnh l cn gi, d mang/xch vi hnh l xch tay. Nn c mt ti nh lun eo bn mnh  ng cc giy t tu thn v giy t quan trng lin quan n nh trng, ngi n</div>\r\n<div>- Kim tra vo sn bay: chun b v my bay, h chiu. Nhn vin hng khng s kim tra giy t, xp ch ngi cho bn trn my bay, lm th tc gi hng nu bn yu cu, kim tra trng lng hng xch tay ca bn xem  hp l cha, dn m s hng bn gi vo mt sau ca v my bay. Nh gi hng n sn bay cui cng trong hnh trnh ca bn. Gi cc phiu ghi m s hng gi cn thn  ly li hng gi khi bn n sn bay cui cng .</div>\r\n<div>- Khai t khai hi quan: bn s c yu cu khai t khai ny  c th xut cnh, ch  khai ng theo mu (giy mu vng, pht min ph ti cc sn bay Vit Nam).</div>\r\n<div>- Mua l ph sn bay: nu cha c gp trong gi v my bay, bn cn mua b sung ph ny, l ph l 14USD, c quy ring  bn l ph ny ngay ti sn bay.</div>\r\n<div>- Kim tra an ninh: tu sn bay, hng ho ca bn s c kim tra an ninh trc hoc sau khi lm th tc bay. Cc nhn vin hi quan v scanner s kim tra xem hng ho bn mang c an ton v hp php khng. V l do an ninh, bn tuyt i khng mang theo cc  cm.</div>\r\n<div>- Kim tra hi quan: nhn vin hi quan s kim tra giy t tu thn, v my bay Bn s c yu cu nu l do xut cnh. i vi cc du hc sinh ln u i n trng, l do ng nhin l du hc v bn cn nh cc thng tin c bn nh: bn hc  trng no, kho hc l g, hc trong bao lu tin nht l a cho h xem th mi hc ca trng.</div>\r\n<div>- Vo phng i: y l phng i trc khi ra my bay. Bn nn ct v my bay, ch gi li th ln my bay trong  ghi cc thng tin v chuyn bay, s gh ngi Tranh th r sot li giy t xem cn  khng, i toalet, hoc c sch trong lc ch i.</div>\r\n<div>- Ra my bay: ch  loa gi hoc xem mn hnh  bit gi ra my bay, ch  xp hng khi ra my bay, sau  ngi ng ch,  hnh l xch tay ln cabin ngay trn u, lm theo cc ch dn ca hng dn vin hng khng v cc vic nh: an ton ti sn, tt in thoi di ng, ch  khi my bay ct cnh, h cnh, bn c th c bo ca hng khng trn my bay, tuy nhin, tuyt i khng ly cc vt dng trn my bay mc d chng c b tr  bn dng khi cn thit, v d phao bi, mt n thng kh Bn c th s b giam gi thm ch ngi t nu vi phm cc quy nh trn.</div>\r\n<div><strong>Ti sn bay Nht Bn</strong></div>\r\n<div>- Khi my bay h cnh, bn nn tm n quy All other passport holders hoc Asian passport holder  lm th tc nhp cnh.</div>\r\n<div>- Cho nhn vin nhp cnh mt cch lch s v a h nhng giy t cn thit gm: h chiu, t khai nhp cnh (thng c pht t trn my bay) v v my bay. C th h s hi bn hc g,  u, hc trong bao lu nn bn hy chun b sn cu tr li hoc giy t  chng minh. Nu h vn thc mc,  ngh h gi n trng ni bn ng k hc  hai bn t gii quyt.</div>\r\n<div>- Bn nh k hiu chuyn bay  ra bng chuyn ly hnh l. Mn hnh v tuyn s ch r hnh l ca bn c tr ti bng chuyn no.</div>\r\n<div>- Tuyt i khng mang h qu ca ngi l gi.</div>\r\n<div>- Bn nn n quy thng tin  nhn vin hng dn bn cch bay tip hoc cch di chuyn v ni bn  bng cc phng tin cng cng nu cn.</div>\r\n<h3>3. in thoi bo cho gia nh bit bn  n ni an ton</h3>\r\n<div>- Gi v my c nh : bm 00 84 + m vng + s c nh, V d, gi v H Ni m vng l 4 bn s bm 00 84 4 + s c nh ca gia nh bn.</div>\r\n<div>- Gi v my di ng : bm 00 84 + s di ng (b s 0 u tin). V d, s di ng ca gia nh bn l 090 xxxxxxx th bn s bm: 00 84 90 xxxxxxx.</div>\r\n<h3><strong>4. To nhanh qu trnh thch ng khi n Nht</strong></h3>\r\n<div>i vi nhng sinh vin xa gia nh hay ra nc ngoi ln u, vn  hc tp tuy c t ln hng u, nhng vic lm quen v thch nghi vi cuc sng mi cng v cng quan trng. iu ny s gip cho nhng thnh cng tip theo trong hc tp v cuc sng x hi ca chnh bn. Nu nh  Vit Nam bn  quen vi cch nghe ging v chp nhn bi ging ri ghi nh th khi du hc, bn s c trng i a ra  kin c nhn hn l ch ghi nh bi ging.</div>\r\n<div>C th m t s iu chnh  thch ng vi vn ho ny theo cc giai on: t mong i mt cch thch th - tht vng, bun nn - h hi n nhn khi  thch nghi vi mi trng mi.</div>\r\n<div><strong>Vy bn s lm g  sn sng vi nhng c sc vn ho ?</strong></div>\r\n<div>- Chun b tt tm l trc khi ln ng, tin rng mnh c kh nng thch nghi tt;</div>\r\n<div>- em theo nh gia nh, sch bo v a nhc yu thch;</div>\r\n<div>- Chia s vi bn b nhng cm xc ca mnh;</div>\r\n<div>- Gp g cc nh t vn cho sinh vin quc t ti trng ca bn khi c vn ;</div>\r\n<div>- Tham gia cc hot ng chung ti trng nh cu lc b th thao, nhm bn ;</div>\r\n<div>- Ti trung tm t vn sc kho khi cn;</div>\r\n<div>- Ch ng lm quen v ho mnh vo cc sinh hot ca lp thng qua cc hot ng trn lp, trong gi gii lao hay cc hot ng thng ny v cui tun ca gia nh nui</div>\r\n<div><strong>C gng:</strong></div>\r\n<div>- Lm quen vi cuc sng mi: Hy bit n gin ho cc chuyn l, th gin, quan st, nghe ngng v tm hiu dn v cuc sng quanh bn, cm nhn nhng khc bit v vn ho nh nhng kin thc mi cn hc hibn s thy mi chuyn khng c g gh gm lm;</div>\r\n<div>- ng gi: tr hn thng b cho l thiu tn trng. Ch  ng gi, hoc l n sm hn, cho d  l mt cuc hn khng my quan trng. Hy gi in bo trc v hy bit ni xin li nu khng th n ng hn..</div>\r\n<div>- Hiu bit v a l: ng ngc nhin nu mt ngi M hay Australia ngh rng ngi Triu Tin ni ting Trung Quc v Columbia l mt thnh ph ca Mexico. Nu h c nhng thng tin khng chnh xc v qu hng ca bn, hy sn lng chia s nhng thng tin v nc mnh.</div>\r\n<div>- Vn ha bt tay v m hn: ci bt tay d vi ai - u c th thay cho mt li cho. Bn cng c th thy nhng bn gi thn thit cho nhau bng cch m hoc hn nh vo m. i khi h cng cho ngi bn khc gii thn vi cch nh vy. Nhng gia nhng ngi n ng vi nhau th khng. Vic bc i tay trong tay hoc khoc vai gia nhng ngi cng gii  nc ngoi l rt him. Nhng ngi l thng trnh chm vo ngi khc, nu chng may trong m ng bn chm phi ai, hy ni xin li.</div>\r\n<div>- Khong cch c nhn: khong cch lch s nn gi khi ni chuyn vi ngi l hoc ngi mi quen thng l 3 bc. Nu bn v tnh thu hp khong cch , h c th cm thy khng thoi mi. Bt c khi no bn cm thy lng tng trong cch x l cc tnh hung, hy quan st nhng ngi xung quanh, v nu chng may c s nhm ln no , bn hy ci v hi whats wrong?</div>\r\n<h3><strong>5. An ton khi du hc Nht</strong></h3>\r\n<div><strong>An ton c nhn: nhng nguyn tc c bn</strong></div>\r\n<div>- Nu thy ngi l mt c nhng hnh vi kh nghi, hy bo cho bo v hoc cnh st  gn bn nht;</div>\r\n<div>- S dng h thng chung bo ng khi cn;</div>\r\n<div>- Nu cn phi i u mt mnh, hy ni vi bn cng phng, gia nh ch nh hay h hng ni bn n v khi no bn s v;</div>\r\n<div>- Lun kho ca phng, t  c khi ra ngoi;</div>\r\n<div>- Lun mang theo TD v lu cc s in thoi khn trong in thoi;</div>\r\n<div>- Khng nn i ra ngoi vi ngi l, ngi mi quen hay ngi say;</div>\r\n<div>- ng c s in thoi ca bn nu c ai gi nhm ti s my ca bn, hy hi h  gi ti s no v khuyn h nn th li;</div>\r\n<div>- ng ni vi ngi gi n l bn ang  mt mnh. Dp my khi nhn phi nhng c in thoi tc tu;</div>\r\n<div>- Khng cung cp thng tin c nhn cho ngi li gi ti;</div>\r\n<div>- Bo vi bo v/ cnh st khi thy nhng mn  b b ri hoc ng nghi;</div>\r\n<div>- Ch mang theo ngi s tin mt cn thit v th tn dng.</div>\r\n<div><strong>Khi i u xa:</strong></div>\r\n<div>-   xung quanh. Trnh i ng tt;</div>\r\n<div>- Khi tri ti, nn i cng ngi quen hoc s dng phng tin giao thng cng cng;</div>\r\n<div>- Chn i nhng ng c h thng sng, gn ng giao thng chnh;</div>\r\n<div>- Ghi nh nhng s in thoi khn cp, chc chn rng c  tin in thoi trong sut chuyn i;</div>\r\n<div>- Nu mang theo v tin, hy gi cn thn bn mnh;</div>\r\n<div>- Khng nghe headphone khi i b mt mnh.</div>\r\n<div>- Nu nhn thy mnh ang b ngi khc bm theo:</div>\r\n<div>- Bng qua ph v i hng i;</div>\r\n<div>- Lun nhn li pha sau  cnh bo mnh  nhn ra h;</div>\r\n<div>- Ghi nh c im nhn dng  c th t li;</div>\r\n<div>- i n khu vc c n sng v ng ngi;</div>\r\n<div>- Thng bo s vic vi bo v hoc cnh st.</div>\r\n<div>- Trong mt to nh</div>\r\n<div>- Khng bc vo thang my cng lc vi ngi c hnh vi kh nghi. Bo li vi cnh st hoc bo v;</div>\r\n<div>- Lun kho ca phng v khi c ngi g ca th phi hi r trc khi m ca;</div>\r\n<div>- Lun gi nhng th c gi tr  ni c kho, khng  lung tung.</div>\r\n<div><strong>Trong xe t</strong></div>\r\n<div>- Kha xe nu bn khng  trong xe t;</div>\r\n<div>- Phi ch  khu vc quanh xe, kim tra sn, gh sau ca xe trc khi ln;</div>\r\n<div>- Nn u xe  ch sng;</div>\r\n<div>- Khng nn  nhng th c gi tr  nhng ch d thy trn xe, nn  vo trong thng xe;</div>\r\n<div>- Khng nn li xe mt mnh vo bui m;</div>\r\n<div>- Khng nn i nh xe trn ng;</div>\r\n<div>- Kho ca xe khi  trong xe v tt nht l ng c ca knh;</div>\r\n<div>- Khi xe hng trn ng, nu c ngi dng li mun gip, tt nht hy nh ngi  gi in gip bn hn l i nh xe;</div>\r\n<div>- Nu nhn thy nh n xanh ca cnh st pha sau, cha nn li xe vo l ng ngay m hy  n ch c nh n - hoc ng ngi, cnh st s hiu s lo ngi ca bn.</div>\r\n<div>- Nu ngh mnh ang b theo di</div>\r\n<div>- Hy n trm cnh st hoc cu ho, k tc x hoc to nh gn nht, hoc ch ng ngi;</div>\r\n<div>- Nu khng c khu vc no an ton gn  th hy bm ci xe tht to.</div>\r\n<div><strong>An ton ti sn</strong></div>\r\n<div>- Lun kho ca phng khi ra ngoi, d ch mt lc.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div style="text-align: right;"><em>Tuyn Hong TMS Edu tng hp</em></div>', '5 iu cn nh trc khi i du hc Nht Bn', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'hoat-dong-noi-bat-1', '', '', '2015-09-22 05:12:18', '2015-09-22 03:12:18', '', 0, 'http://localhost/demowp/wallbase/?p=180', 0, 'post', '', 0),
