(182, 1, '2015-07-31 05:47:35', '2015-07-31 03:47:35', '<div><a href="http://nhatban.net.vn">Nht Bn</a> - Thp nin 90, mt bo co nhan  Mt quc gia lm nguy c cng b  M nu bt nhu cu ci cch gio dc ti<a href="http://duhocnhatban.com.vn/">Nht Bn</a>. Lnh o hai nc M v Nht tn thnh rng cn phi c mt cuc nghin cu, so snh nn gio dc gia hai nc. Sau , mt cuc hp thng lng u tin c t chc  Kyoto c 24 nc tham d, kt qu: C 2 bn bo co c cng b.</div>\r\n<div>Trong mt bn, cc nh nghin cu M bo co v nhng im mnh v im yu ca Nht Bn, cn cc bn bo co kia, cc nh nghin cu Nht Bn cng tin hnh tng t nh vy i vi nn gio dc ca M.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div><strong>T nhng tiu chun ngt ngho.</strong></div>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n Nht, hu ht cc trng tiu hc u l trng cng, ch c khong 0,7 trng tiu hc l trng t. Cc trng trung hc c s cng vy, c n 97% l trng cng v ch c 3% l trng t. C khong 27% trng trung hc ph thng l trng t. Hc sinh  khu vc no phi theo hc  trng khu vc y, mun hc khc tuyn cng khng c.<a href="http://duhocnhatban.com.vn/">Nht Bn</a>ang c gng tiu chun ho trnh  gio vin trn ton quc  m bo cht lng ging dy. <a href="http://duhocnhatban.com.vn/">Nht Bn</a>c 50 huyn, mi huyn chu trch nhim tuyn gio vin cho huyn mnh. Mt gio vin nm nay c th ph trch dy lp 1, nhng nm sau c th dy lp 3 hay lp 5. Cng thng xuyn quay vng vic dy cng nh chuyn dy t trng ny sang trng khc.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n<strong>Vi nhng nghin cu su rng</strong>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\nT chc nh gi gio dc quc t  tin hnh hai cuc kho st so snh cht lng hc tp ca sinh vin trn ton th gii. Kt qu l <a href="http://duhocnhatban.com.vn/">Nht Bn</a>, s khc bit v nng lc v thnh tch hc tp ca sinh vin gia cc trng l ti thiu, c l l t nht trn th gii. Hu ht sinh vin, hc sinh Nht Bn u lm ch chng trnh hc.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\nCc chuyn gia gio dc<a href="http://duhocnhatban.com.vn/">Nht Bn</a> c nhiu d n nghin cu v tnh hnh kinh t  x hi cng nh vn ho lch s, li sng ngi dn  tm ra chng trnh gio dc ph hp nht cho mi cp. Ngi Nht rt d ng vi vic em h thng gio dc nc khc p dng vo nc mnh. C th  cng l mt yu t a<a title="h thng gio dc Nht Bn " href="http://duhocnhat.com.vn/he-thong-giao-duc-nhat-ban.html">h thng gio dc Nht Bn</a>c c nhiu chun mc ring.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n<strong>n truyn thng hc tp</strong>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div>V sch gio khoa, cc cng ty xut bn lin h vi cc gio s v ging vin cc trng i hc chuyn v mn hc no   chun b sch gio khoa. Nhng cun sch ny s trnh ln B Gio dc thng qua. Tiu chun thng qua da trn cc kho hc do B t chc. Ch c nhng cun sch no p ng c tiu chun mi c a vo th nghim s dng  trong nh trng. B c mt b phn chuyn trch tuyn chn sch gio khoa cho tng cp hc, kh nghim tc. Nu thanh tra gio dc khng thng qua cun sch no , th cun sch  khng c php s dng trong nh trng.Tuy nhin, vn c s khc bit kh ln v thi  ca ngi phng Ty vi ngi Nht i vi sch gio khoa. Hu ht ngi Nht khng ngh sch gio khoa ch l cng c, m chng cn hm cha truyn thng, nhng vn  l lm th no t thot ra khi nhng thi  truyn thng i vi sch gio khoa, v sch gio khoa m ch mang ni dung truyn thng s lm cho hc sinh s khi buc phi nh tt c nhng thng tin . Nu khng sa i s khng th ci thin gio dc, c bit nhng mn hc x hi. Ngy nay, nhng ngi bin tp sch gio khoa  c mt quan im r rng: Chnh hc sinh, sinh vin l nhng ngi s dng tht s nhng cun sch gio khoa , cn gio vin ch to iu kin thun li cho vic hc tp ca hc sinh m thi.</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: right;">Du hc Nht Bn su tm</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: right;">ngun: Thng tin t vn i du hc Nht</div>', 'Gio dc Nht bn: Nhng chun mc thnh cng', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'hoat-dong-noi-bat-2', '', '', '2015-09-22 09:31:01', '2015-09-22 07:31:01', '', 0, 'http://localhost/demowp/wallbase/?p=182', 0, 'post', '', 0),
