(195, 1, '2015-08-03 05:50:51', '2015-08-03 03:50:51', '<strong>Trung tm o to v Pht trin quc t (ITC) trc thuc trng i hc Nng Lm  i hc Thi Nguyn c nhim v xy dng v trin khai cc chng trnh hp tc quc t, trong  c bit u tin tm kim c hi cho sinh vin tham gia cc chng trnh Thc tp ngh nghip, vic lmv du hc nc ngoi.</strong>\r\n\r\nTham gia chng trnh Thc tp ngh nghip, vic lm v du hc nc ngoil c hi tuyt vi cho cc bn tr nng cao ngoi ng, tch ly kin thc, kinh nghim, k nng lm vic v thu nhp, p ng yu cu ngun nhn lc cht lng cao trong thi k hi nhp Quc t su rng.\r\n\r\nTrung tm o to v Pht trin Quc t  Trng i hc Nng lm Thi Nguyn thit lp quan h hp tc vi nhiu t chc Quc t v hin ang trin khai thnh cng nhiu chng trnh thc tp ngh, vic lm v du hc ti cc nc nh: Nht, M, Israel, Philipin, i LoanTrong thi gian ti, trung tm s tip tc m rng nhng chng trnh ny sang cc nc khc nh c, Ailen, Hn Quc, Canada.', 'Gii thiu chung va hc va lm', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '36-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-08-03 05:50:51', '2015-08-03 03:50:51', '', 36, 'http://localhost/demowp/wallbase/2015/08/03/36-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
