(282, 11, '2015-09-16 09:26:20', '2015-09-16 07:26:20', 'Lm thm ngoi gi l c hi cho ngi lao ng kim thm thu nhp tch ly, ph gip gia nh. Tuy vy, khng x nghip no ng vin ngi lao ng nn lm thm gi, v nh vy v lu di s nh hng n sc khe ca ngi lao ng. Nhng i vi ngi lao ng ngoi nc, y c coi l thi gian vng bc, do khng cn dnh thi gian cho gia nh, khng vui chi gii tr, c tp trung ton b thi gian v sc lc cho mc ch chnh kim tin l iu khin ngi lao ng thy tha mn nh.\r\n<div id="bodytext" class="details-content clearfix">\r\n\r\n<strong>Thi gian lm thc t</strong>\r\n\r\nTrong hp ng m cc thc tp sinh k vi x nghip tip nhn. Mi nm, s gi lm vic ca ngi lao ng dao ng t 1.920  2.064 ting/nm. Tc l trung bnh mi thng ngi lao ng phi lm bnh qun l 20 n 21,5 ngy/thng. Vy cc bn lm g trong nhng ngy cn li? Thm na, ngoi 8 ting/ngy cc bn c mun lm thm hay khng?\r\n\r\n<strong>Thu nhp t mi gi lm thm</strong>\r\n\r\nX nghip Nht tr lng rt sng phng, lng ngi lao ng c tnh theo gi, lm thm 1 gi c tnh lng 1 gi. Theo Lut lao ng Nht Bn quy nh th mi gi lm thm bng 130% gi lm bnh thng, lm m v cc ngy ngh, l tt c nhiu s thay i, ln ti 200%.\r\n\r\n<strong>Cao do khng tr ph ph</strong>\r\n\r\nMi gi lm thm khng b tr bt c khon ph no, gn nh l khong tin b ra ca ngi lao ng. VD: Bnh qun mi gi x nghip tr ngi lao ng 750 yn/gi, thu nhp khong 130.000 Yn/thng (tng ng 27,5 triu ng). Tr tt c ph ph, bo him, n  cn  li c 19 triu ng. Nu mi ngy lm thm 2h (trong 22 ngy/thng lm vic, ngh ch nht v th 7), c thng s c 44h lm thm. Tng cng ngi lao ng  thm c 42.900 Yn (tng ng 9 triu). Nh vy s  ra c 28 triu /thng .  c th  ra c 40-50tr/thng l c th, nhng nh vy cc bn phi lm kh vt v.\r\n\r\n<img class="aligncenter" src="http://japan.net.vn/images/uploads/2014/01/28/1369014998.jpg" alt="" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Lm thm t u?</strong>\r\n\r\nNhiu nm lm vic vi cc bn thc tp sinh, rt nhiu bn c ti hng dn lm h s, t chc thi tuyn, theo di thi gian lm vic bn Nht, thanh l h s khi v nc\r\n\r\nNhiu bn c nhn thc rt sai lm v vic lm thm khi sang Nht. VD nh:\r\n\r\n- Ngnh nng nghip khng c vic lm thm? Mt s hc vin  sang Nht vn k l h phi lm vt v n 9-10h ti trong nh knh, hoc dy t 2-3h sng  x l hoa, rau, c, qu cho kp gi sng xe ca cng ty n vn chuyn i. Tt nhin s vt v ca cc bn u c tr thu nhp xng ng\r\n\r\n- Nghnh xy dng kh lm thm? iu ny do cc bn nhn vo ngnh xy dng  cc vng qu ti Vit Nam, nu sng mt thi gian trn cc thnh ph ln cc bn s thy nhng ta nh c ngy khng c mt bng ngi nhng c cao ln tng ngy, thc cht l cc thnh ph ch cho php xe xy dng ra vo t 20h m n 6h sng.  Nht cng vy, nghnh xy dng rt pht trin,  m bo tin  d n, ngi cng nhn nhiu khi phi lm c ngy m. Vn  duy nht nm  sc khe ca ngi lao ng\r\n\r\n- X nghip khng cho lm thm? Mt s x nghip s khng cho lm thm do vic hot ng khng cn thit phi lm thm. Nhng phn nhiu khi tip nhn lao ng nc ngoi x nghip  ang rt cn nhn cng, mi x nghip khi tip nhn lao ng ngoi nc  Nht u c chnh quyn kim sot rt cht, t l lao ng nc ngoi v lao ng trong nc u m bo rt nghim ngt, lun tun th cc ch  i vi lao ng nc ngoi.\r\n\r\n- Khng ng chuyn mn khng c lm? Vic lm thm n t nhiu khu on, x nghip tip nhn ca cc bn thng rt ln v c nhng lc v tr ny cn ngi, c lc v tr khc. V d, trong x nghip xy dng gm cc b phn chnh nh: ct thp, dn gio cp pha, xy chat, p lt. Khi tuyn, x nghip thng phn r ly bao nhiu ngi cho v tr ct thp, bao nhiu ngi cho v tr dn gio. Tt nhin cng vic th ai lm c xy dng u gn nh l bit c, khng th trong thi gian lm vic cng nhau s hc c.\r\n\r\nNgay c nhng cng vic hu cn, dn dp nh xng, lau chi cng c cng hon ton c th tnh vo gi lm thm ca cc bn. Nhng n ph thuc nhiu vo thi  lm vic, mi quan h trong x nghip, ch x nghip,...\r\nH tr t nhiu pha\r\n\r\nKhi phng vn vi cc x nghip cc bn c th hiu c l x nghip tip nhn hon ton bit r mc ch sang Nht lm vic ca cc bn, hiu c cc bn mong mun nhng g v lm th no  p ng c nhng mong mun . Ch cn cc bn lm tt cng vic, lm h hi lng th vic  ngh c lm thm gi, tng lng l rt d dng.\r\n\r\ny l nhng vn  kh nhy cm cng vi vic ngn ng ca ngi lao ng cn rt km nn nhng trng hp thu nhp khng tt ngi lao ng c th nh n s gip  ca nghip on. Cng ty ang c hn 20 nhn vin qun l thc tp sinh ti Nht nn khng kh khn g trong vic hng dn thc tp sinh mi, h tr trong sinh hot v cng vic.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="aright source" style="text-align: right;"><strong>Tc gi bi vit: </strong>THANHPT</div>', 'Lm thm ngoi gi l ngun thu chnh ca Thc tp sinh', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'lam-them-ngoai-gio-la-nguon-thu-chinh-cua-thuc-tap-sinh', '', '', '2015-09-16 09:26:20', '2015-09-16 07:26:20', '', 0, 'http://thuctapsinhktm.vn/?p=282', 0, 'post', '', 0),
