(328, 11, '2015-09-22 09:31:01', '2015-09-22 07:31:01', '<div><a href="http://nhatban.net.vn">Nht Bn</a> - Thp nin 90, mt bo co nhan  Mt quc gia lm nguy c cng b  M nu bt nhu cu ci cch gio dc ti<a href="http://duhocnhatban.com.vn/">Nht Bn</a>. Lnh o hai nc M v Nht tn thnh rng cn phi c mt cuc nghin cu, so snh nn gio dc gia hai nc. Sau , mt cuc hp thng lng u tin c t chc  Kyoto c 24 nc tham d, kt qu: C 2 bn bo co c cng b.</div>\r\n<div>Trong mt bn, cc nh nghin cu M bo co v nhng im mnh v im yu ca Nht Bn, cn cc bn bo co kia, cc nh nghin cu Nht Bn cng tin hnh tng t nh vy i vi nn gio dc ca M.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div><strong>T nhng tiu chun ngt ngho.</strong></div>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n Nht, hu ht cc trng tiu hc u l trng cng, ch c khong 0,7 trng tiu hc l trng t. Cc trng trung hc c s cng vy, c n 97% l trng cng v ch c 3% l trng t. C khong 27% trng trung hc ph thng l trng t. Hc sinh  khu vc no phi theo hc  trng khu vc y, mun hc khc tuyn cng khng c.<a href="http://duhocnhatban.com.vn/">Nht Bn</a>ang c gng tiu chun ho trnh  gio vin trn ton quc  m bo cht lng ging dy. <a href="http://duhocnhatban.com.vn/">Nht Bn</a>c 50 huyn, mi huyn chu trch nhim tuyn gio vin cho huyn mnh. Mt gio vin nm nay c th ph trch dy lp 1, nhng nm sau c th dy lp 3 hay lp 5. Cng thng xuyn quay vng vic dy cng nh chuyn dy t trng ny sang trng khc.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n<strong>Vi nhng nghin cu su rng</strong>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\nT chc nh gi gio dc quc t  tin hnh hai cuc kho st so snh cht lng hc tp ca sinh vin trn ton th gii. Kt qu l <a href="http://duhocnhatban.com.vn/">Nht Bn</a>, s khc bit v nng lc v thnh tch hc tp ca sinh vin gia cc trng l ti thiu, c l l t nht trn th gii. Hu ht sinh vin, hc sinh Nht Bn u lm ch chng trnh hc.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\nCc chuyn gia gio dc<a href="http://duhocnhatban.com.vn/">Nht Bn</a> c nhiu d n nghin cu v tnh hnh kinh t  x hi cng nh vn ho lch s, li sng ngi dn  tm ra chng trnh gio dc ph hp nht cho mi cp. Ngi Nht rt d ng vi vic em h thng gio dc nc khc p dng vo nc mnh. C th  cng l mt yu t a<a title="h thng gio dc Nht Bn " href="http://duhocnhat.com.vn/he-thong-giao-duc-nhat-ban.html">h thng gio dc Nht Bn</a>c c nhiu chun mc ring.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n<strong>n truyn thng hc tp</strong>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div>V sch gio khoa, cc cng ty xut bn lin h vi cc gio s v ging vin cc trng i hc chuyn v mn hc no   chun b sch gio khoa. Nhng cun sch ny s trnh ln B Gio dc thng qua. Tiu chun thng qua da trn cc kho hc do B t chc. Ch c nhng cun sch no p ng c tiu chun mi c a vo th nghim s dng  trong nh trng. B c mt b phn chuyn trch tuyn chn sch gio khoa cho tng cp hc, kh nghim tc. Nu thanh tra gio dc khng thng qua cun sch no , th cun sch  khng c php s dng trong nh trng.Tuy nhin, vn c s khc bit kh ln v thi  ca ngi phng Ty vi ngi Nht i vi sch gio khoa. Hu ht ngi Nht khng ngh sch gio khoa ch l cng c, m chng cn hm cha truyn thng, nhng vn  l lm th no t thot ra khi nhng thi  truyn thng i vi sch gio khoa, v sch gio khoa m ch mang ni dung truyn thng s lm cho hc sinh s khi buc phi nh tt c nhng thng tin . Nu khng sa i s khng th ci thin gio dc, c bit nhng mn hc x hi. Ngy nay, nhng ngi bin tp sch gio khoa  c mt quan im r rng: Chnh hc sinh, sinh vin l nhng ngi s dng tht s nhng cun sch gio khoa , cn gio vin ch to iu kin thun li cho vic hc tp ca hc sinh m thi.</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: right;">Du hc Nht Bn su tm</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: right;">ngun: Thng tin t vn i du hc Nht</div>', 'Gio dc Nht bn: Nhng chun mc thnh cng', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '182-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-09-22 09:31:01', '2015-09-22 07:31:01', '', 182, 'http://thuctapsinhktm.vn/2015/09/22/182-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(329, 11, '2015-09-22 09:39:09', '2015-09-22 07:39:09', 'Mt s du hc sinh ti Nht chia s rng, sau k ngh, nu lm vic tht chm ch v bit tit kim, c khi s kim c gn 80 triu VN mt thng.i vi sinh vin i du hc th vic i lm thm dng nh  tr thnh mt iu tt yu. Bi i lm khng ch gip sinh vin trang tri c cuc sng ni x ngi, m cn l c hi, iu kin  tip xc thc t vi i sng ca ngi bn x.\r\n\r\nV t nc mt tri mc ny ngy cng c cc bn la chn lm im n  hc tp. Nu so vi nhng t nc khc th cuc sng ca ngi Nht kh t . Tuy nhin, khng v th m nhiu bn li t b am m du hc ca mnh.\r\n\r\nNhiu sinh vin i theo dng t tc hoc hc bng, sau khi qua Nht n nh tnh hnh ch  th bt tay vo tm kim vic lm. Ty vo iu kin ca tng ngi m c bn qua  c 1 thng th i lm, c bn n 3, 4 thng sau mi c vic.\r\n\r\nVic i lm thm  Nht kh hp dn vi sinh vin, cc bn c th tm cho mnh mt cng vic nh bn hng trong siu th, phc v qun n, c ph, pht bo, lm trong cc x nghip. Lng lm thm  Nht tnh theo gi,<strong>trung bnh 700  1.200 Yn/gi, tng ng vi 180.000 ng  320.000 ng.</strong>Bn c th lm<strong>4 ting 1 ngy nhng khng c qu 28 ting 1 tun.</strong>y l quy nh  Nht, v h s rng nu sinh vin lm thm qu nhiu s nh hng n vic hc. y cng l mt trong nhng tiu cc khi sinh vin i lm thm.\r\n\r\nTi mt s thnh ph ln nh Tokyo, Osaka mc lng thng cao hn. Tuy cao nhng a s cc bn cng ch  sng ti . Gi c v mc lng ph thuc vo mc  gn hay xa trung tm thnh ph. D mc sng  Nht kh t , nhng nu chu kh i lm thm v tch gp th ngoi vic t tr hc ph, tin sinh hot th c kh nhiu bn  dnh dm gi tin v nh.\r\nMinh Tun, 20 tui, ang l sinh vin ca trng H Phc Li Nagoya cho bit:<em>Vic lm thm  y kh a dng, ty thuc vo nng lc ca bn l N3, N2, N1 m c nhng mc lng khc nhau. Nu bn c N2, th xin vic lm d dng hn, bn c th kim trn<strong>1.500 Yn/gi.</strong>Cn nu bn c N1, ngha l trnh  giao tip ca bn by gi  nh ngi bn x, th bn c th lm phin dch ti cc cng ty, hi ngh vi mc<strong>3.000 Yn/gi</strong>. Vy nn, nu mun tm cho mnh mt cng vic lng cao th yu t nng lc ting Nht ca bn phi tt. Trung bnh 1 thng th bn c th lm trn 2.000$.</em>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://duhochoasen.com/wp-content/uploads/1339207613-cua-hoc-vua-lam-them-cung-du-hoc-sinh-nhat-1.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-77" title="Lam them Nhat Ban" src="http://duhochoasen.com/wp-content/uploads/1339207613-cua-hoc-vua-lam-them-cung-du-hoc-sinh-nhat-1.jpg" alt="alt" /></a> mt s nc, ngi ta cm khng cho sinh vin i lm thm, iu ny rt l bt tin. Tuy nhin,  Nht th li kh thong, chnh ph Nht to mi iu kin  bn c th i lm thm. Theo quy nh chung th sinh vin khng c i lm qu 28 ting 1 tun v phi c giy php ca c quan xut nhp cnh. Nhng bn ng c lo, khi hc  trng, ta s c nh trng to iu kin  bn i lm, s cp giy php cho bn i. Bn cnh  th bn c th lin h vi i s qun Vit Nam ti Nht  c h tr tt nht.\r\n\r\nMt kinh nghim c bt m na l ngi Nht rt trng ch tn. V th bn s c li khi c ngi quen gii thiu. Mi i lm ban u, bn nn chm ch i lm vo cc ngy cui tun. Bnh thng cui tun, bn c th lm nhiu hn v lng cng nhnh hn. Vo cc dp l, tt, cc bn sinh vin thng  li m khng v. y l c hi  kim tin nhiu hn, lng vo cc ngy l cng tng gp 2, 3 ln so vi bnh thng. Sau mt k ngh nhiu bn c th kim c vi trm ngn Yn, khong<strong>300.000 Yn</strong>l gn 80 triu Vit Nam ng. y qu l mt s tin khng nh vi sinh vin.\r\n\r\nNhiu bn va i hc va i lm  c  kh nng trang tri ton b hc ph ca mnh m khng cn n gia nh. Mt s bn dnh dm mi thng c khong 20 triu,  l tr ra ton b sinh hot ph. Lng  Nht kh cao, nhng ci gi ca n cng khng h r cht no, bn phi lm ct lc v tht chm ch. Ngi Nht nh gi tnh nghim tc v k lut kh nghim khc nhng h cng nh gi cao kh nng c gng ca bn. Gii ting Nht l mt li th  xin vic vi mc lng cao.\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><em>Lam Giang</em></p>', 'Chong vi tin lm thm ca du hc sinh ti Nht', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'choang-voi-tien-lam-them-cua-du-hoc-sinh-tai-nhat', '', '', '2015-09-22 09:39:09', '2015-09-22 07:39:09', '', 0, 'http://thuctapsinhktm.vn/?p=329', 0, 'post', '', 0),
