(344, 11, '2015-09-25 05:49:05', '2015-09-25 03:49:05', '<strong>Cng ty TNHH KTM (KTM) trc thuc trng Trung cp Kinh t - Ti nguyn v Mi trng c nhim v xy dng v trin khai cc chng trnh hp tc quc t, trong  c bit u tin tm kim c hi cho sinh vin tham gia cc chng trnh Thc tp ngh nghip, vic lmv du hc nc ngoi.</strong>\n\nTham gia chng trnh Thc tp ngh nghip, vic lm v du hc nc ngoil c hi tuyt vi cho cc bn tr nng cao ngoi ng, tch ly kin thc, kinh nghim, k nng lm vic v thu nhp, p ng yu cu ngun nhn lc cht lng cao trong thi k hi nhp Quc t su rng.\n\nCng ty TNHH KTM (KTM) - Trng trung cp Kinh T - Ti nguyn v Mi trng  thit lp quan h hp tc vi nhiu t chc Quc t v hin ang trin khai thnh cng nhiu chng trnh thc tp ngh, vic lm v du hc ti cc nc nh: Nht, M, Israel, Philipin, i Loan...Trong thi gian ti, trung tm s tip tc m rng nhng chng trnh ny sang cc nc khc nh c, Ailen, Hn Quc, Canada....', 'Cm nang chia s xut khu lao ng', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '47-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-09-25 05:49:05', '2015-09-25 03:49:05', '', 47, 'http://thuctapsinhktm.vn/2015/09/25/47-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
