(354, 11, '2015-09-28 09:40:04', '2015-09-28 07:40:04', '<div class="separator"><a href="http://thongtinduhoc.info/du-hoc-nhat/" target="_blank"><strong>Du hc Nht Bn</strong></a> hin nay ang l cch m nhiu hc sinh, sinh vin Vit Nam la chn  thay i tng lai. Vy <strong>du hc Nht Bn</strong> c thc s lm c iu ? Khng t ngi Vit  v ang t ra cu hi ny. Bn ngh, cuc sng ni t khch xa hoa, lng ly. Bn ngh s sung sng, hc tp ni y. Xin hy loi b nhng suy ngh mu hng y v quay tr li hin thc. i vi nhiu ngi, <strong>du hc Nht Bn</strong> khng ch  nng cao tr thc, m cn l mt s tri nghim. Cn vi bn th sao?</div>\n<div class="separator">Khng t ngi b l nhng c hi  thay i cuc sng ca mnh v ngn ngi phi vt qua nhng th thch v nh i nhng g ang c  dc sc vo nhng thnh qu cn cha kp nh hnh. Tt c nu gi h vi nhng g mnh ang c, tha mn vi chng m khng tm kim nhng g mnh thc s mong mun. <strong>Du hc Nht Bn  Nu mun thnh cng th ng ngi nhng kh khn.</strong></div>\n<div class="separator"><a href="http://thuctapsinhktm.vn/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/16.jpg"><img class="size-full wp-image-355 aligncenter" src="http://thuctapsinhktm.vn/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/16.jpg" alt="16" /></a>\n<h3><strong>1. Mi kh khn chnh l mt c hi tim n</strong></h3>\n<div></div>\n<div><em>Cuc i ta nh mt hn , chnh bn l ngi quyt nh  hn  y ph rong ru hay tr thnh vin ngc ta sng</em> Cavett Robert</div>\n<div></div>\n<div>Cuc sng vn khng h bng phng m lun cha ng nhng vt v, thch thc dnh cho tt c chng ta. V i ngi l cuc hnh trnh vt qua nhng th thch . Hy hng v pha trc. Bn ng vi nn ch, mi ln vt qua mt kh khn, bn s thy mnh trng thnh hn. V cch tt nht  nh gi nng lc ca mt ngi l nhn vo cch ngi   vt qua nhng kh khn tr ngi trong cuc sng. Sau cng, kh khn gian kh s em li cho mi ngi mt ti sn v gi   l s trng thnh v tri nghim.</div>\n<div><a href="http://intraco.edu.vn/du-hoc-nhat-ban/" target="_blank"><strong>Du hc Nht bn</strong></a> cng ging vy. N khng hon ton mu hng nh bn vn ngh. Cuc sng hc v sinh hot ni y lun tn ti nhng kh khn nht nh. Kh khn v thi gian, kh khn v hc tp, kh khn v chi tiu,Nhng bn c bao gi ngh, nhng kh khn y ang y bn xung bn ly, hay y l c hi  c hi  bn c th hin bn thn, c hi  bn n lc l chnh mnh.</div>\n<div>Ai cng mun cng vic ca mnh c sun s, khng gp rc ri no c  ti tin l vy. Th nhng, kh khn li thng xy ra vo nhng lc khng ng nht. Trc kh khn, nhiu ngi thng than thn trch phn sao mnh bt hnh n vy nhng c nhng ngi li ch mm ci v bt u ngh cch gii quyt. c nhng ngi ch mi gp cht rc ri, h  thay i thi , thm ch ri vo bi quan, chn nn. Ngc li, c nhng ngi li xem kh khn xy n l c hi, l th thch, nh l thng ca cuc sng. H lun c nim tin vo mt vin cnh ti sng v sn sng ng u, thch thc vi chng v quyt tm phi vt qua.</div>\n<div>Nu bn ang c  nh <strong>du hc Nht Bn</strong>, ti khuyn bn hy cn nhc tht k. iu ti mong bn cn nhc chnh l thi  bn thn bn trc cc kh khn. Bi l,  u, lm g, tt c u tim n nhng kh khn nht nh.</div>\n<div></div>\n<h3><strong>2. Chp nhn kh khn hay  kh khn nhn chm</strong></h3>\n<div></div>\n<div>Mt trong nhng cha kha ca thnh cng l khng c b cuc d hon cnh c tr nn ti t n u chng na  v mi vn  sau cng lun s tm c cch gii quyt. y l mt thng ip quan trng chng ta thng c nghe thy, nhng li thiu bn lnh khi p dng vo thc t khi kh khn xy ra.</div>\n<div>Nh chng ta  bit, du hc l con ng tri di v khng h bng phng. N lun tim n nhng kh khn m yu cu bn phi n lc ht mnh  vt qua. Hn th na, Nht Bn li l nc c nn gio dc pht trin, hc tp kht khe. Bn c  bn lnh  xua ui kh khn khng? Hay im lng v ch i s kh khn y nhn chm gi tr ca bn.</div>\n<div>Ti chc rng, khi quyt nh i du hc, cng chnh l lc bn ang m tng v mt tng lai rng m. Tng lai y c m ra hay khng, n hon ton nm trong tay bn. Bn c s nhng kh khn? Bn c bao gi im lng trc n? Hay chn nn, hay bn cho rng mnh khng  sc  vt qua.Hy b nhng suy ngh y i, ng dy nhn v pha trc, t tin vi cu ni:Ti lm c!.</div>\n<div><strong>3. Khi gp kh khn  mi ngi s c mt cch khc nhau</strong></div>\n<div>ng nh cu ni:Hc tp l con ng ngn nht dn n thnh cng nhng cng l con ng kh khn nht  i n n.</div>\n<div>Vi s kht khe, khng ngng i mi ca nn gio dc. Nht Bn l c th gii nh gi l t nc c nn gio dc pht trin thuc top th gii. C l c hc tp ni y tht s l mt c hi ln i vi hc sinh, sinh vin cc nc, c bit l Vit Nam. Nhng khng ch c vy, ni y lun tn ti nhng kh khn m du hc sinh no cng khng trnh khi. C ngi kh khn v tin bc, c ngi kh khn v p lc cuc sng  hc tp, c ngi kh khn v cc mi quan h bn b  ngi thn,Tt c u c th n vi bn bt c lc no.</div>\n<div>Bn c s phi vt qua ni s hi? Bn  bao gi t nh:Ti ch l mt ngi bnh thng, ti cng chng c mt ng lc no hay s c v tinh thn no c.Ti phi tha nhn rng, y chnh l nguyn nhn ln nht khin bn khng mnh dn vn ln v dn tht bi. C th ni, y l suy ngh i xung ca a s ngi Vit.</div>\n<div>Khi gp kh khn, bn c nhn thy nhng c hi tim n?Hy nh rng con ng duy nht chc chn dn n tht bi l khng n lc g c.Mi ngi u c mt kh nng v mt hon cnh ring, nn con ng vt qua nghch cnh  vn n thnh cng cng khng ging nhau  ngoi tr sc mnh ca  ch, nim tin v lng dng cm.</div>\n<div></div>\n<div>Chc chn bn cng c cch ca ring mnh  vn ti thnh cng . Bn c tt c mi th tim n   c th vt ln s phn v thnh cng . Ti sao khng thc hin cho chnh mnh ?</div>\n<div><strong>Tng kt:</strong></div>\n<div>Suy cho cng th lm vic g,  bt c ni u, u c nhng kh khn nht nh.  vt qua hay b dm xung l  bn. Bn c th ng ln, tm con ng ring v gii quyt vn . Bn cng c th im lng, ch i hoc khng lm g. Nhng ti ngh rng, khi  quyt nh du hc, th chc rng bn  chun b cho mnh khng t tm l, tng lai. Bn c mun tng lai ca mnh rng m? Bn c mun thnh cng? Hy ng dy, t tin v ni:Ti lm c!.</div>\n<div>Chc cc bn thnh cng trn con ng hc tp!</div>\n</div>\n<div class="separator"></div>', 'Du hc Nht Bn  Mun thnh cng th ng ngi kh khn', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '184-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-09-28 09:40:04', '2015-09-28 07:40:04', '', 184, 'http://thuctapsinhktm.vn/2015/09/28/184-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
